<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-B6699589-69D1-4279-874A-FF95A284DE74" version="3" lang="en-US"?><reference xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-B6699589-69D1-4279-874A-FF95A284DE74" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic reference)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c reference oceReference-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic       reference/reference "><title class="- topic/title ">Dashboard for partners</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-914ADA3D-E522-44B2-A738-89D9569EC893"><p class="- topic/p "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Dashboard for Partners</b> </p><p class="- topic/p "> Dashboarding requires the correct configuration of the SOID. </p><p class="- topic/p ">The SOID indicates the ownership of the service contract. If this is not set to the partner, the machine will not appear in the dashboards of the partner. Details on how a SOID must be used can be found in the functional description document. See 
<xref class="- topic/xref " keyref="FUNCSOID001" href="GUID-D046B792-D44D-4E62-B14F-AA4F626FE00B.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="reference"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>Sales/Service Organization IDentifier (SOID)</xref>.</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Functional description</category></metadata></prolog><refbody class="- topic/body        reference/refbody "><section id="GUID-87767D45-D63A-468B-BC90-CB2E6343E904" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Workflow and actions to support a correct dashboard for partners</b> </title><fig id="GUID-DFAAB52C-C883-4C8F-9595-649A21CC4E2A" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Workflow</title><image href="GUID-B4514688-EAA9-42FB-8061-29368D815483-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B4514688-EAA9-42FB-8061-29368D815483-svg.svg"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Additional information (Access required):</p><table id="GUID-7D5047D0-895B-4336-856C-7CAF2C170EE8" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="*" class="- topic/colspec "/><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> User Manual - Service Organization Administration</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref href="https://servicemd.cpp.canon/DocsAndTools" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot gentext?>https://servicemd.cpp.canon/DocsAndTools</xref></p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Service master data portal</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref href="https://servicemd.cpp.canon" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot gentext?>https://servicemd.cpp.canon</xref></p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> ORS (On Remote Service) portal</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref href="https://service.cpp.canon" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot gentext?>https://service.cpp.canon</xref></p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-6157A4A7-01DB-425B-99EF-E30102818957" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Set customer information</title><fig id="GUID-2220904B-5E93-4E01-B493-3F0C8E081850" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Workflow</title><image href="GUID-84692CA8-76B6-4248-AF70-D43573CBDFD6-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-84692CA8-76B6-4248-AF70-D43573CBDFD6-svg.svg"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-5F9AD684-E48B-421D-985C-0E923C6123C0" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to change customer information </title><p class="- topic/p "> The generic customer information can be found in the service mastedata. Changing customer information is described in "UserManual - Products-Customer/Contacts" that can be found in 
<xref href="https://servicemd.cpp.canon/DocsAndTools" scope="external" format="html" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot usertext?>https://servicemd.cpp.canon/DocsAndTools</xref></p><p class="- topic/p "> To be able to add/change information the rights for " Author Local for Customer/Contact functionality" needs to be coupled to your account. </p><p class="- topic/p ">In case this is missing, the menu item Customer/Contact is not present or the import button is not shown.</p><fig id="GUID-C52AA55E-9C9A-4E6F-8317-1D860A336C5B" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-7AF95706-47AB-4A55-BD55-35C28B4BC4FD-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7AF95706-47AB-4A55-BD55-35C28B4BC4FD-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Currently there is no possibility to edit in the view. </p><p class="- topic/p ">Changing customer information is done via importing the customer information again. See the UserManual for the template and howto.</p><fig id="GUID-20777F86-B4AB-4208-B6F3-5E79EF8449C1" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Example</title><image href="GUID-8C49AFB0-193F-4A93-97D9-2349825ED7EA-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-8C49AFB0-193F-4A93-97D9-2349825ED7EA-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> The side effect of changing customer information this way is that the previous customer information is also still present. </p><p class="- topic/p ">This implementation might change. So please check the User Manual on updates on the changing of customer information.</p></section><section id="GUID-9F7235EE-9413-4C28-A785-9847DE5D5F96" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to set contact information of customer and machine </title><p class="- topic/p "> Login on the ORS portal ( 
<xref href="https://service.cpp.canon" scope="external" format="html" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot usertext?>https://service.cpp.canon</xref> ), search and select the machine. </p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select Remote data, </p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select Management information, </p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Add customer contacts and </p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">If applicable: add machine contact information.</p></li></ol><fig id="GUID-953B0238-C24A-4D92-888F-A4A0FD1231E5" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-F68BAF27-B5B3-4ADB-A698-8AE604045B27-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F68BAF27-B5B3-4ADB-A698-8AE604045B27-low.png"/></fig></section></refbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-15596943-D29F-470F-B4B7-04F9215760AD.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Dashboarding</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
